    "causal_summary": "This sub-phase investigates whether Modus-style BM25 field weighting is worth exposing or tuning inside Public's constrained lexical retrieval path. It studies field-mapping, benchmark design, and operator visibility while preserving Public's current hybrid architecture. It does not approve BM25 as a replacement for hybrid retrieval.",
